This file marks the location of the MainScene.unity for the Saba MMD Viewer.

When opened in Unity Editor, create the scene with:
- Main Camera with CameraController component
- Directional Light
- Canvas with UIManager component
- ModelLoader GameObject
- FilterManager GameObject (attached to camera)
- EnvironmentManager GameObject
- BoneController GameObject
- AnimationController GameObject
- RecordingManager GameObject
- GobotIntegration GameObject
- LanguageManager GameObject (singleton, DontDestroyOnLoad)